    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to MessagePack Module</title>

      <para>
        <application>MessagePack</application> is an efficient binary
        serialization format. It lets you exchange data among multiple
        languages like JSON. But it's faster and smaller. This package
        provides CPython bindings for reading and writing MessagePack data.
      </para>

      &lfs120_checked;

